{"tid":677919,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"相集銷量稱冠　西野七瀨被爆緋聞贈興","createTime":"2018-05-25T15:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T16:02:13.000Z","uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3251edfa45ff490cbe1ad2c1bf65f57320c9bf11","tid":677919,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180520183734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180520183734&h=fc07a95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本人氣女團乃木坂46的23歲主將西野七瀨，近日推出到摩洛哥取景的個人首本相集《我的事情》，收錄身穿比堅尼及內衣上陣的性感寫真，由於反應熱烈，出版社已兩度加印應市，而作品首周亦勁賣9.2萬本，成功登上Oricon一周書籍銷量榜的冠軍，相當威水！ <br />\n<br />\n而雜誌《週刊文春》選擇在此時爆料贈興，在昨晚一個網上節目指，兩年前西野七瀨跟一名男子過從甚密，她於2016年4月24日晚上讓男方到香閨過夜，約一星期後男方再在西野寓所逗留5小時，直至深夜約1時兩人結伴外出。雜誌近日查出該名男子是30多歲的電視節目導演，於是日前在街頭追問西野真偽，不過西野未有回答便離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001_02p.jpg?20180520183734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20180520183734&h=a4190074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西野七瀨日前在街頭被追問緋聞，不過她未有回應。"},{"pid":"e27e4af9f8a9ca107c2af342a4fba146aefd74e3","tid":677919,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/mobile/bkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001.html&d=B3ifCGddofe07YKHAYxKP1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=5b488738\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/mobile/bkn-20180520181058660-0520_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c1b8b69eb969127e6886f0a6bafdc38d58d12e28","tid":677919,"uid":89507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"係姬係公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd820eae0b4278e70ef9752fbbd4526e4eb3fd73","tid":677919,"uid":112316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:02:13.000Z","msg":"娜娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}